Privacy Policy:
Last updated: November, 12, 2021

Definitions:
Hardware ID: The unique ID that is on your headset.

Headset: The device you are running the game on.

I: The developer.

Use of data:
I collect your hardware ID - it is being used for authentication until i get a better system set up.

I am networking your head and both hands position and rotation including your microphone (used for voice chat), you can disable the microphone in the prompt that comes you when you start the game for the first time.
